usage: image_corpus.py [-h] [-a] [-g] [-r ROWS] [-c COLS] [-t {jpg,tif,bmp,png}] indir [outdir]

Process images for an image corpus.

positional arguments:
  indir                 Input directory
  outdir                Output directory

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -a, --aspect          Preserve aspect ratio
  -g, --grayscale       Save as grayscale
  -r ROWS, --rows ROWS  Number of rows in output image
  -c COLS, --cols COLS  Number of columns in output image
  -t {jpg,tif,bmp,png}, --type {jpg,tif,bmp,png}
                        Output image type